Wallet size phone listsI will be passing out ETS mailing Omahas to Ann for distribution updated walletsize phone list The list includes blackberry numbers Below please find directions to set your blackberrys to be notified of only high priority messages All other messages will reach your blackberry but you will not be disturbed by routine messages A person notifying you will have to indicate that the message is high priority If you have any problems let me know Run the Desktop Manager Double click on Redirector Settings Select the Filters tab Select New Type a filter name whatever you makeup for this exercise click on Importance and change drop down box to High Click the box Forward with Level Notification Click ok apply ok Now go to the handheld device and choose Options Choose Notify then move down to Level Notify Only and make sure it indicates Yes Iris S Waser Enron Transportation Services Company Smith Street EB b Houston TX fax

URGENT Enron Kids ChristmasHi everyone There are oodles of Kids who are not being adopted Please reach as deep into your pockets as you can so that we can perhaps adopt a second Kid What we will be providing them has been reduced to get more people interested in assisting Now the Kids will not get a new pair of shoes or coat Some of you have already generously contributed Thank you Some of you have adopted a Kid all by yourself Fabulous Please give your contribution to Ruth or me The shopping will be handled for you Thanks Ruth and Iris

A Christmas Carol Charles Dickens at The Alley TheatreI have discount tickets to see A Christmas Carol at The Alley Theatre on Sunday December th at pm A Seating is per person B Seating is per person and Gold Circle is per person Sorry not much notice I must have your money by the end of today Iris
